Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:39.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eso es algo de ti que realmente odio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,¿Nunca has visto estrellas antes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Me llamo Takatou Keisuke.
